# CODEOWNERS file for Application Repository
# This file lists who must review updates made to the application.

# Rule 1: Default owners for the application
# Any change not matched by a specific rule will be reviewed by these owners
* @app-owner @app-backup

# Rule 2: Business logic and core features
# Files that control how the application works
/app/ @app-owner

# Rule 3: User-facing components
# Files that affect screens, pages, and user interactions
/ui/ @ui-owner
